{"tid":2257372,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳華強北火熱改裝 iPhone 12！網民：iPhone 11 改頭換面可用多兩年","createTime":"2020-10-25T06:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T23:56:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f235fbc02fc5ce1aef6eb63935a4d590640d58ef","tid":2257372,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2780000/2783726/20201022_iphone12_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2780000%2F2783726%2F20201022_iphone12_01_1024.jpg&h=e0ded500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2783726?=1200&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yJhHPiZq5Mrnvt1M0WQd-_nuiEQnAdnqxDpIzQOUODYCNdD5BIOy1Rik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2783726%3F%3D1200%26fbclid%3DIwAR0yJhHPiZq5Mrnvt1M0WQd-_nuiEQnAdnqxDpIzQOUODYCNdD5BIOy1Rik&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PRVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=ee403c2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2783726?=1200&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yJhHPiZq5Mrnvt1M0WQd-_nuiEQnAdnqxDpIzQOUODYCNdD5BIOy1Rik</a>"},{"pid":"efd94e9c6a118ac61602ea452e31c12996e9a2cc","tid":2257372,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"iPhone 12、iPhone 12 Pro 兩款新 iPhone，早前未開賣之際，深圳華強北竟已驚現「iPhone 12」於市面出售！？原來，這些在華強北野生捕獲的 iPhone 12，並非真正 Apple 出品，而是最近於這處流行的改裝版本。<br />\n<br />\n早前，深圳華強北雖未有出售 iPhone 12，但這裡的商戶已流行將舊 iPhone 型號改裝為 iPhone 12，成為現時最 hit 產物。有華強北商戶表示，基本上凡是舊 iPhone 都可改裝為 iPhone 12 的模樣，只要將顧客現正使用的 iPhone 組件，全都放進 iPhone 12 機殼（當然是山寨出品）之中，再對好各項組件的線路鋪排便可。留意的是，有部分 iPhone 型號當改裝為 iPhone 12 後，或會出現部分功能缺失的情況，如雙鏡頭拍攝的話，就只有單個鏡頭可用。<br />\n<br />\n華強北改裝 iPhone 12 商機之所以促成，是自上月初開始就已有 iPhone 12 玻璃背板、屏幕、鏡頭等零件流通市面，有網友笑指將 iPhone 11 改為 iPhone 12 後，多用兩年都沒有問題。收費方面，iPhone 11 會較便宜，盛惠約 100 人民幣（約 HK$118）；iPhone X 會昂貴一點，收費為 450 人民幣（約 HK$531），而改裝 iPhone 12 價格高低，就視乎有否 iPhone 排線而定。"},{"pid":"55f1d844a41d91c2b59dfb30e9379e7cdb4555ee","tid":2257372,"uid":76804,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"有部分 iPhone 型號當改裝為 iPhone 12 後，或會出現部分功能缺失的情況，如雙鏡頭拍攝的話，就只有單個鏡頭可用。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01600e8a130ceb765a535ac2f4de7846dc6eb569","tid":2257372,"uid":265925,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:26:33.000Z","msg":"又幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c437709989d48d886e2e1382055b8aaa561cb0","tid":2257372,"uid":92787,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"反智到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ip11原本就可以用幾年"},{"pid":"598ac44483784ef6dd1823b8d55b20eff9900f51","tid":2257372,"uid":65638,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"支那真係好識創新"},{"pid":"d719bbb54635540c4ab3fe6704d42604160bc98c","tid":2257372,"uid":41130,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"戴完套都分唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba486ac8774565b135d50a15018bcd0caaea3b1","tid":2257372,"uid":7147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"我老友向華強北"},{"pid":"d8d394bd438389ed0516ed2fcf51890f6b20b30d","tid":2257372,"uid":31773,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多此一舉<br />\n<br />\n呢個國家永遠得個殼真係見微知著"},{"pid":"2112ae0453e394f9adf41190d0b9ee3bdf0aec79","tid":2257372,"u